text: Franz Scherübl (born 23 November 1940) is an Austrian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Austria Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Radstadt
